    "It exploits the stacked layers of the transformer to attend to the information beyond the window size.",
    "It yields a 2× speed improvement over a vanilla attention baseline.",
    "The Rolling Buffer Cache can roll with the span of the window limit and can overwrite the past values to stop cache size increases.",
    "The Pre-fill and Chunking can pre-fill the key and value pair from the cache for a faster prompt.",
    "With very large prompts, it is easy to chunk it.These engines can serve as the baseline for many areas of research focus."
